---
title: "ApiSchemaTable"
description: "Astro shell renders the full schema tree at build time; a tiny Preact island (client:idle) toggles expand/collapse on the existing DOM via event delegation."
type: interactive
---

# ApiSchemaTable

An interactive hierarchical table for displaying API parameters, request body fields, or response fields. Supports nested objects, union types, and expand/collapse.

The schema tree is fully rendered server-side, so the entire field hierarchy is in the static HTML even before hydration. The companion `ApiSchemaTableNav` island only flips BEM modifier classes and the `hidden` attribute on rows that are already in the DOM — it never receives the schema as a prop.

## Properties

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `fields` | `string` (JSON) | — | JSON string of `SchemaField[]` |
| `title` | `string` | — | Optional heading above the table |
| `showExpandAll` | `boolean` | `true` | Show the Expand All / Collapse All button |

## Examples

### Flat fields

{% schemaTable fields="[{\"name\":\"dashboard_id\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"The ID of the dashboard.\"},{\"name\":\"title\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Title of the dashboard.\"},{\"name\":\"is_read_only\",\"type\":\"boolean\",\"required\":false,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":true,\"description\":\"Whether the dashboard is read-only.\"}]" title="Path Parameters" /%}

### Nested fields

{% schemaTable fields="[{\"name\":\"data\",\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"The main data wrapper.\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"type\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"The resource type.\",\"enumValues\":[\"dashboards\"]},{\"name\":\"attributes\",\"type\":\"object\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Dashboard attributes.\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"title\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Title of the dashboard.\"},{\"name\":\"description\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Description of the dashboard.\"}]}]}]" /%}

### Deprecated and required fields

{% schemaTable fields="[{\"name\":\"old_field\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"deprecated\":true,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"This field is no longer used.\"},{\"name\":\"api_key\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Your API key.\"}]" /%}

### Enum values

{% schemaTable fields="[{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"deprecated\":false,\"readOnly\":false,\"description\":\"Sort order for results.\",\"enumValues\":[\"asc\",\"desc\",\"name\",\"-name\",\"created\",\"-created\",\"modified\",\"-modified\"],\"defaultValue\":\"asc\"}]" /%}
